---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Minimal habit tracker · memoato"
  description="A minimal habit tracker designed for fast logging, clear progress, and a simple daily timeline."
  canonicalPath="/minimal-habit-tracker"
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h1 class="page-title">A minimal habit tracker</h1>
      <p class="muted">Track what matters. Skip the overhead.</p>

      <p>
        memoato is built for people who want results without turning habit tracking into a second job. It keeps the
        workflow simple: quick capture, clear feedback, and a timeline you can scan.
      </p>

      <h2>What “minimal” means here</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Fast capture</strong>: log entries in seconds.</li>
        <li><strong>Sane defaults</strong>: templates reduce setup and decision fatigue.</li>
        <li><strong>Readable progress</strong>: charts and totals make the signal obvious.</li>
        <li><strong>Daily timeline</strong>: review your day by category without digging.</li>
        <li><strong>Forgiving workflow</strong>: miss a day, keep going.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Try it</h2>
      <p>
        Start with 2–3 categories (Weight, Water, Push ups), set a simple goal, and check the timeline at the end of the
        day.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn primary" href="https://app.memoato.com" rel="noreferrer" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">Open app</a>
        <a class="btn" href="/help">Help & FAQ</a>
        <a class="btn" href="/blog/why-memoato">Read the story</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

